=<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Team Member Alert</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset and Base Styles */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Container */
        .email-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border-top: 5px solid #805AD5; /* Purple for "Alert/Lead" context */
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 30px 10px 30px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #edf2f7;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #2D3748;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .badge {
            background-color: #ebf8ff;
            color: #3182ce;
            font-size: 12px;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Content Body */
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .intro-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        /* Member Profile Mini-Card */
        .profile-summary {
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .avatar-placeholder {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            background-color: #cbd5e0;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }

        .profile-details h4 {
            margin: 0 0 4px 0;
            color: #2d3748;
        }

        .profile-details p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #718096;
        }

        /* Checklist Section */
        .checklist-container {
            background-color: #fffaf0; /* Light orange background for attention */
            border-left: 4px solid #ed8936;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
        }

        .checklist-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #c05621;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .checklist-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .checklist-checkbox {
            min-width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border: 2px solid #ed8936;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-right: 12px;
            margin-top: 3px;
            background-color: white;
        }

        .checklist-text {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #4a5568;
        }

        /* Button */
        .btn-container {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: #2D3748;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #a0aec0;
            border-top: 1px solid #edf2f7;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                width: 100%;
                border-radius: 0;
                border-top: none;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-container">

            <div class="header">
                <h1>New Member Alert <span class="badge">Engineering</span></h1>
            </div>


            <div class="content">
                <p class="intro-text">
                    Hello Team Lead,
                </p>
                <p class="intro-text">
                    A new team member has just completed the intake process and has been added to Slack and Asana. They are ready for their first day!
                </p>


                <div class="profile-summary">
                    <div class="avatar-placeholder">NM</div>
                    <div class="profile-details">
                        <h4>{{ $json.fields.Name }}</h4>
                        <p>{{ $json.fields.Department }} · Joined Today</p>
                    </div>
                </div>


                <div class="checklist-container">
                    <div class="checklist-title">⚡ Immediate Actions Required</div>

                    <div class="checklist-item">
                        <div class="checklist-checkbox"></div>
                        <div class="checklist-text"><strong>Send a welcome DM</strong> on Slack to break the ice.</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="checklist-item">
                        <div class="checklist-checkbox"></div>
                        <div class="checklist-text"><strong>Schedule a 1:1</strong> for this week to align on expectations.</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="checklist-item">
                        <div class="checklist-checkbox"></div>
                        <div class="checklist-text"><strong>Assign an onboarding buddy</strong> to help them navigate the codebase.</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="checklist-item">
                        <div class="checklist-checkbox"></div>
                        <div class="checklist-text"><strong>Review pending Asana tasks</strong> to ensure they have access to the right projects.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="btn-container">
                    <a href="#" class="btn">View Onboarding Checklist</a>
                </div>
            </div>


            <div class="footer">
                <p>Automated by HR Ops System</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
